info.author: Sean Kelly
classifiers: Topic :: Software Development :: Libraries :: Python Modules
info.description:
*************
pdsvex.policy
*************

This is the policy product for pdsvex.policy.  It orchestrates the
dependencies necessary in order to run a PDS Venus Express profile server.


.. References:
.. _buildout: http://pypi.python.org/pypi/zc.buildout
.. _Plone: http://plone.org/
.. _Python: http://python.org/download/releases/2.4.6/
.. _PIL: http://www.pythonware.com/products/pil/
.. _download: http://plone.org/products/plone


Installation
============

Add ``pdsvex.policy`` to the list of eggs for your Zope 2 instance, or make it
the dependency of an egg in your Zope 2 instance.


Changelog
=========


2.0.0 — Upgrades
----------------

Seriously updated for Zope 2.13.21 and Plone 4.3.2.


1.0.1 — 2009.7.16 — Documentation
---------------------------------

This release addresses an issue where documentation for the profile server
wasn't appearing.  It does now!


1.0.0 — FCS
-----------

First customer ship.


0.0.0 — Unreleased
------------------

Initial release.
